gw.api.effdate

Interface UniqueOnPolicyPeriod

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    APDPolicyInvolvedParty, BAJurisdiction, BAPolicyContactRole, BOPPolicyContactRole, CPPolicyContactRole, GLPolicyContactRole, IMPolicyContactRole, PAPolicyContactRole, PlcyNonPriNamedInsured, PolicyAddlInsured, PolicyAddlInterest, PolicyAddlNamedInsured, PolicyBillingContact, PolicyContactRole, PolicyDriver, PolicyLaborClient, PolicyLaborContractor, PolicyLocation, PolicyNamedInsured, PolicyOwnerOfficer, PolicyPriNamedInsured, PolicySecNamedInsured, WCLaborContact, WCPolicyContactRole

    public interface UniqueOnPolicyPeriod
    This interface declares 2 methods to assist in generating EffDatedUniqueKeys and the error messages associated with finding duplicate keys. Entities that implement this interface should also consider adding all instances of that entity on the PolicyPeriod to the EffDatedUniqueKeyGenerators property of PolicyPeriodBaseEnhancement which will allow the validation code to automatically generate errors when duplicates are found.
